original_title: Amy Winehouse: 45th At Night (MTV): Amy Winehouse
overview: Amy Winehouse with The DapKings TRL Studios, New York City, NY, USA, 2007 45th At Night  Here’s Amy performing at the MTV's Times Square studios as part of the 45th at Night live series.  Amy's backing band were the Dap Kings while Amy also performs Love Is A Losing Game in part with Mos Def.  This is the set list for Amy's MTV's 45th at Night performance...  Back To Black - 00:45  Love Is A Losing Game - 5:05  Rehab - 9:00  Me And Mr. Jones - 12:33  Tears Dry On Their Own - 15:10  You Know I’m No Good - 18:17
tagline: Amy Winehouse - 45th At Night (MTV's Times Square studios as part of the 45th at Night live series)
